EverClassify introduces a new way to shop online classifieds, letting you broaden your shopping horizons to any scale so you can find the best deals available exactly where you need them.

Buy and sell online and smartly look for exactly what you want and where you want it, so you can grab the best deal going. Building on top of EverClassify's dynamic location-aware search function with smart-granular filters, results are presented in a friendly, quick-scan view making it faster and easier than ever to find what you're looking to buy or sell your items faster to more buyers. Find whatever you're looking for, wherever you're looking for it, right now with EverClassify.

EverClassify or EC is a unique classified experience. What sets us apart:

EC allows sellers to advertise locally and nationally by setting a visibility, sellers perspective EC allows buyers to search locally and nationally by setting a visibility, buyers perspective EC provides options to display items in a gallery EC provides premiere ad options EC provides search capabilities to finds items instantly EC provides sellers the option to see post analytics EC provides an optional silent bid system for buyers to anonymously interact with sellers EC provides an optional silent bid system allowing seller to award a bid to whom they choose EC provides options for sellers to post in more than one location or multi-city posting

Coming soon - global launch and event or new post notification for sought after items.
